Nemesis Enforcer:



The winged Predacon finally reached the ship's storage bay after making a 
wrong turn and getting lost for several minutes.  He stopped at the bay's 
door, which didn't open.

"Blasted thing must be damaged..." Nemesis muttered, punching the door as 
hard as he can to break it open but the door is so strong he only makes a 
dent.  He takes a few steps back and charges the door, slamming into it with 
his shoulder.  The door collapsed inward, Nemesis crashing down on top of it. 
 "Ha..." he murmured, trying to collect himself from the impact.

He got up, searching around the bay for several moments and collecting as 
much of the supplies Megatron had wanted that he could carry.  He activated 
his comm. and established a comm-link with Megatron. "Meg, this is Nemesis 
Enforcer.  I got the junk you wanted, so where do you want me to take them?"
